# nim-skill is local-first: NONE of these are required on the default path.
# The reliability trio (guard, error-handler, monitor, enforcer) runs fully offline.

# Optional: forward monitor error/reject events to Sentry (graceful no-op if unset or @sentry/node absent).
# SENTRY_DSN=

# Optional: directory for the file(JSONL) monitor sink and dashboard history.
# Default: .nim/traces.jsonl in the current working directory.
# NIM_TRACE_FILE=.nim/traces.jsonl
